<h3 id="structure">Structure</h3>

<h4 id="mvc-and-rails-apps">MVC and Rails apps</h4>

<ul>
  <li>Rails follows the MVC structure for applications. A request is sent over the web, it makes its way to our Rails app, then what? How does the app take that request and get the necessary data and/or perform the necessary task?</li>
</ul>

